reviews.text: You can get good quality modern breads in Yuen Long area
Great quiche and cheese tart. Americano and chocolate are both nice.

They have many funny types of bread. There is also a deck which only sells bread or cakes just baked. The best thing is the little corner which serves coffee and smoothies. I would say it’s not a simple bakery.
Very good bakery, aromatic and attractive. Nice seating on large tables for casual afternoon refreshments and coffee. Inside shopping center next to cinema.
Cheese tart was heavily cheesy &  delicious; but tuna bun is stone cold & the bottom crust was burnt. 27 dollars for them... should be higher quality!
